# Global Layoffs Data Analysis
 📌 Project Overview

This project explores global layoff data using SQL, Python, and Power BI to uncover trends across industries, companies, countries, and time periods.

🎯 Objectives

- Clean and prepare the dataset
- Perform exploratory data analysis
- Identify layoff trends
- Analyze industries and countries
- Build an interactive Excel dashboard
 🛠️ Technologies
- Excel

 📊 KPIs

- Total Layoffs
- Layoffs by Country
- Layoffs by Industry
- Layoffs by Company
- Monthly Layoff Trend
- Percentage of Employees Laid Off

 📈 Key Insights

- Technology companies experienced the highest layoffs.
- Layoffs peaked during economic downturns.
- The United States recorded the largest number of layoffs.
- Several industries recovered over time.

 📂 Files

- layoffs analysis.xlsx

